<HEADLINE> Romania's Industry, Building, Trade Recover </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The survey was conducted on the basis of the answers by the
managers of the companies in the three activity fields, the
official Rompres news agency reported on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
As much as 37 percent of those interviewed expect the
industrial production to continue growing, while more than half of
the companies think the production bulk and the orders portfolio
are likely to keep the same level as that of the term before.
</P>
<P>
