during the third term as well. It will be higher for the ready-
mades, rubber processing, the plastics industry and the industry
putting out other non-metallic products. The prediction is made by
the big companies with more than 500 employees but also by the
small and medium size ones working in several industrial fields.
</P>
<P>
The building sector along with the state-run companies and
those owning private capital, will keep their ascending activity
trend. Managers of the specific companies predict an additional
stock of contracts and orders.
</P>
<P>
The retail is also expected to have a positive development
which means a rise in the commodities' sales, the survey says.
