<HEADLINE> Saudi Arabian Businessman Visits West China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 2 (Xinhua) -- President of the Shamrany Group
of Saudi Arabia Al Shamrany reached 20 cooperation agreements with
Chinese enterprises during his visit to Gansu province in west
China.
</P>
