by the International Volleyball Federation:
</P>
<P>
Group A: China, Brazil, Japan, United States in Macao (August 4-
6)
</P>
<P>
Group B: Cuba, Russia, South Korea, Italy in Thailand (August 4-
6)
</P>
<P>
Group C: Brazil, Russia, Japan, Italy in Chinese Taipei (August
11-13)
</P>
<P>
Group D: China, Cuba, South Korea, United States in Malaysia(
August 11-13)
</P>
<P>
Group E: China, Cuba, Japan, United States in China (August 18-
20)
</P>
<P>
Group F: Brazil, Russia, Italy, South Korea in Philippines(
August 18-20)
</P>
<P>
Grand Finale: all eight teams in Philippines (august 24-27).
</P>
