<HEADLINE> HK Gold Price Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, August 2 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
dropped two Hong Kong dollars to close at 2,576 HK dollars a tael
Wednesday, according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold
dealers in Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
