<TEXT>
<P>
JERUSALEM, August 2 (Xinhua) -- Israel's Knesset, or Parliament,
Wednesday morning passed a bill calling for dissolving the Knesset
and holding a new election, another blow to Israeli Prime Minister
Ehud Barak and his peace efforts.
</P>
