pilgrims and civilians massacred at a pilgrim camp at Pahalgam
town in west Kashmir on Tuesday evening, 18 laborers shot dead in
Anantnag district in west Kashmir late Tuesday night and a seven-
member family of a surrendered militant, which was wiped out by
militants in the frontier district of Kupwara in north Kashmir
