<HEADLINE> China Starts Producing Color TFT LCD </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CHANGCHUN, August 2 (Xinhua) -- Changchun City in northeast
China has started batch production of color liquid crystal display
(LCD) with thin film transistors (TFT).
</P>
<P>
The production line and technology of the TFT-LCD project were
introduced from abroad, which were currently in operation at the
Toshiba and IBM corporations.
</P>
<P>
Construction of the production line started in September 1998
in Changchun, capital city of northeast China's Jilin Province.
</P>
<P>
The products will be used in mobile phones, positioning and
guiding systems for automobiles, mini-VCD and DVD players, and
notebook computers.
</P>
<P>
The producer has signed contracts of intent worth of 4.8
billion yuan with over 20 corporations.  
