<TEXT>
<P>
NANJING, August 2 (Xinhua) -- More than 430 foreign artists
will participate in the Sixth Chinese Arts Festival scheduled
between September 28 and October 10 in Nanjing, capital of east
China's Jiangsu Province.
</P>
