defeated his rival Shimon Peres from the Labor Party in Monday's
presidential election with a surprise 63-57 vote, said that
tensions existing between the right- and left-wing factions, the
old and new generations as well as those between the Jews and
Arabs should be eliminated. (Israel-Presidential Inauguration)
