<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 2 (Xinhua) -- Chinese young parents are able to
ask about every detail of child care by logging onto Goodbaby.com
with 200 experts online.
</P>
<P>
The website, launched by Goodbaby Corporation two weeks ago,
largest producer of child commodity in China, caters to parents,
especially those with children aged from zero to six, according to
Tuesday's China Youth Daily.
</P>
