<HEADLINE> Arafat Meets S. African Foreign Affairs Minister </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, August 3 (Xinhua) -- Palestinian leader Yasser
Arafat was holding private talks with South African Foreign
Affairs Minister Nkosazana Dlamini-Zuma in Pretoria, the South
African Foreign Affairs Department said in a statement on Thursday
